"{\"uid\": \"yardbarker.com-olympics-articles-katie_ledecky_is_now_the_most_decorated_us_womens_athlete_in_olympic_history-s1_13132_40690013\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Katie Ledecky continued to add to her incredible legacy on Thursday at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katie Ledecky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katie_Ledecky\"}, {\"begin\": 99, \"end\": 104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998842270155, \"rank\": 1.157729221898661e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thanks to Team USA's silver medal in the 4X200 meter freestyle relay, Ledecky was able to collect her 13th Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.862698323312495, \"rank\": 0.08506556081717111, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That now makes her the most decorated women's athlete in American history.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 304, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 287, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American history\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/History_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ledecky swam the third leg of Thursday's relay, finishing it in 1:54.93.\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 378, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday Ledecky won the 1,500 freestyle by posting an Olympic record to give her eight career Olympic golds and 12 total medals.\", \"from\": 380, \"to\": 513, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That moved her into a tie with Jenny Thompson, Dara Torres and Natalie Coughlin for the most medals in American women's Olympic history.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 546, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jenny Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jenny_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_Torres\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dara Torres\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_Torres\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dara_Torres\"}, {\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalie_Coughlin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Natalie Coughlin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalie_Coughlin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Natalie_Coughlin\"}, {\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.8338730624977592, \"rank\": 0.19818144526729836, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thursday's relay put her in sole possession of first place.\", \"from\": 652, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has a chance to add to her total this weekend when she competes in the 800 freestyle.\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When it comes to Ledecky's greatness, it is not just about the number of medals she has accumulated in her career.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is also one of the most dominant Olympians ever with the way she wins.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is not uncommon to watch her races where she is the only person on camera in the pool because she is so far ahead of every other competitor.\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1138, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That was the case with Wednesday's 1500 race.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old might not be done with the Paris games, either.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1229, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999998842270155, \"rank\": 1.157729221898661e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shehas said repeatedlythat she is eyeing the 2028 games in Los Angeles where she would have an opportunity to keep adding to her total.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999304097291171, \"rank\": 6.849491452169672e-05, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Gretzis a freelance writer based in Pittsburgh.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1428, \"end\": 1438, 